<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Madcap" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Madcap,</orth> a fellow of wild and eccentric habits: <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 5, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.160" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 160</bibl>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>the merry m. lord,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 2.215" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 215</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a m. ruffian,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.290" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 290</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the m. duke,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.244" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 244</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the m. Prince of Wales,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 95</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>